Package: https-keyscript
Version: 0.0.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Adam Watkins <adam.gc.watkins@gmail.com>
Description: A keyscript and initramfs-tools helpers to allow a machine with a LUKS-encrypted boot drive to passwordlessly boot by fetching a remote key over HTTPS.
Depends: cryptsetup (>= 2), wget (>= 1.15)
Recommends: keyutils (>= 1.5)
